This, Customer InfoData Card App, project was made with node.js.

We cannot read styleSheet.css file using node.js yet. This problem would be handled soon.

2020/06/10
Use 'fs.readFile' for reading customer data file.
USe 'fs.readdir' and read customer name for making customer list.

2020/06/12
Use 'fs.rename' and fread queryString value, we can add new customer data and edit some data.
Use 'fs.unlink', we can remove any selected customer data.
Make home button for going main home.